If you are an electrician, carpenter, plasterer, plumber, air conditioning or satellite specialist. Register now on “AnaMehani” and offer your services to clients who need home maintenance services.
AnaMehani app provides you with a simple friendly user experience.
-Set yourself free from restricted working hours; work wherever and whenever you desire.
-Show your experience and skills in the work gallery section, so clients can trust you and make you one their preferences whenever they need help.
-Reach clients easily and quickly via the GPS feature.
- Continuously browse your previous activities to check your achievements.
-Provide your services in more than one area according to your preferences through the multiple locations feature.
-Do your job professionally, make clients satisfied and get high ratings so you can rank up and get more job opportunities.
- Rate your experience with clients to help us improve service quality for you.
